reviewText: This film MUST be seen by all humans on our planet! UFOs are here! They are real! They are seeking to kidnap our unsuspecting airline passengers (and hippies)! The government knows these facts, yet keeps them hidden deep within the bowels of the Earth! Who are the OVERLORDS OF THE UFO? This crucial question is answered now! The evidence is clear! Hear the experts reveal their secrets! Are the "aliens" from an invisible dimension of the universe? Is a Watergate-sized cover-up involved? All is unveiled in this great film! NASA is hiding the truth that we have a right to know! Why are satellites disappearing??? Obviously, we are NOT alone! Watch and believe!...
